278
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,399
Tapi, semuanya sudah berakhir sekarang.

279
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:32,399
Karena mobil di sebelahnya dipindahkan,

280
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:35,599
